graph TD
    Start([Start]) --> ID[Enter Patient ID]
    ID --> Choice{Select Action}
    Choice -- 1: Appointment --> Clinic[Select Clinic & Doctor]
    Clinic --> Slots[Loop: Select Time Slot]
    Slots --> SMS[Confirm & Send SMS]
    SMS --> Another
    Choice -- 2: Test Results --> Exists{Tests Exist?}
    Exists -- No --> NoTest[Display: No Records]
    Exists -- Yes --> Ready{Results Ready?}
    Ready -- No --> Wait[Display: Waiting Message]
    Ready -- Yes --> View[Display & Download PDF]
    View & NoTest & Wait --> Another{Another Action?}
    Another -- Yes --> Choice
    Another -- No --> End([End])
